# ==========================================
# HEALTH CHECK
# ==========================================

### Health Check
GET {{base}}/health


# ==========================================
# FASE 3 — Auth
# ==========================================

### Cadastro de novo usuário
POST {{base}}/client
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lucas Rosa",
  "email": "lucas@rosabet.com",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "password": "senha123",
  "phone": "11999999999"
}

###

### Login com usuário demo (já existe ao subir em development)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo@rosabet.com",
  "password": "demo123"
}

###

### Meu perfil (requer token)
GET {{base}}/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Atualizar perfil (requer token)
PUT {{base}}/client
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lucas Rosa",
  "username": "lucasrosa",
  "phone": "11999999999",
  "currency": "BRL",
  "notification_sms": true,
  "notification_email": false
}

###

### Atualizar senha (requer token)
PUT {{base}}/client/password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_password": "demo123",
  "new_password": "nova123"
}

###

### Ativar / desativar conta (requer token)
PUT {{base}}/client/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}


# ==========================================
# FASE 4 — Eventos esportivos
# ==========================================

### Listar todos os eventos abertos (ao vivo + pré-jogo)
GET {{base}}/sport/open

###

### Listar eventos ao vivo (filtra no cliente a partir do mesmo endpoint)
# Dica: todos os eventos com is_live=true são os ao vivo
GET {{base}}/sport/open


